793 932 Ethnic Albanians comprise 90 percent of the population in Kosovo , but Serbs maintain control through a large military and police presence .
933 1043 Serbian police say they are trying to eliminate the pro-independence Kosovo Liberation Army and restore order .
1044 1174 At least 51 people were reported killed in clashes between Serb police and ethnic Albanians in the troubled region in recent days .
